      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone needing a solid daily driver. While the engine and drivetrain are functioning as expected, the exterior shows its age with some clear coat peeling on the roof and a few minor scuffs on the rear bumper. Inside, the upholstery has some light wear and a small tear on the driver's side bolster, but all electronics and climate controls are fully operational. This is an honest car for someone who prioritizes utility over a perfect aesthetic.",
