    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained sports sedan offers a perfect balance of performance and daily usability. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, showing only the minor stone chips expected from careful road use, with no significant dents or scratches. Inside, the premium leather upholstery remains supple and clean, with minimal wear on the driver\u2019s side bolster and a completely smoke-free environment. All technological features, from the responsive navigation system to the premium audio and dual-zone climate control, function exactly as intended. Mechanically, the vehicle is in excellent health, benefiting from a fully documented service history, a recent oil change, and a fresh set of tires. It drives straight, shifts smoothly through all gears, and provides a confident, engaging experience behind the wheel. This is a turn-key example, professionally detailed and ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
