      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty ride and it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my trips. I\u2019ve made sure to keep up with the maintenance, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with its next owner! It looks great and drives even better. Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
