      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. This driver\u2019s specimen features the desirable 6-speed longitudinal manual transmission and a factory-calibrated limited-slip differential. The chassis dynamics are sharp, benefiting from recent subframe reinforcement and a refreshed multi-link rear suspension setup. While the exterior displays minor road-derived patina, the powertrain remains potent, delivering a linear torque curve and that signature metallic rasp through the quad-exit exhaust. A well-sorted example for the purist seeking authentic steering feedback and atmospheric performance.",
